# THE BIGGEST IMPROVEMENT IN TERMAIL EVER!!!
  A NEW GENERATION OF FIDONET MAIL-READER IS BORN!!!

+ INTERNAL-MESSAGE-EDITOR now built-in.
  Insert the keyword InternalMsgEditor and if you do not want to use
  an external editor. Help is on F1.
  Scrollbar, margin etc. can be defined.
  In other words, the Fidonet mailreader that has everything you will ever
  need for reading and writing mail.

+ Everything is much faster....
+ Internal autocorrect function TM.CRT will correct up to 500 words/group
+ Alt-Z MEGA search, will search all conferences and save result.
+ Signature manager on F5 in internal editor (TM.SIG)
+ Best message reformatting using TM.RFM definitions also on Ctrl-B
  Mew keywords: ReformatQuotes and ReformatAsk
+ Increased maximum number of areas from 500 to 1000
+ Advanced MOUSE support, including fileattach, viewfiles, help etc.
+ Quote warning level can be defined, 50% percent default
* Increase reading of JAM-indexes by 700% meaning that scanning your JAM-areas
  on a network drive will now work much faster.
+ Stylecolors. 15 different colors in your messages to substitute bold,
  italic, underline and reverse and combinations. Press Alt-Y to insert in
  internal message editor.
+ Support for the new JAR (.J) and ACE (.ACE) format for packing/unpacking mail
+ Higlighting of internet email addresses, www pages and ftp sites.
+ Call spellchecker directly in internal editor
+ SendLog, keeps track of all the messages you write
+ ROT13 encryption/decryption on Alt-U
+ Import markers inserted when importing files into internal editor
+ Addressbook group handling (G)
+ Addressbook sorting in 6 ways (G)
+ Addressbook now has www-homepage and can call up the web-browser
+ Search for www-pages inside message and call web-browser directly
+ New function Alt-M, Uplink maintenance
+ Searchword in text will now FLASH making it easier and faster to locate
+ GIF-kludge support enabled
+ Support for external utilities with MSGINFO.SYS created before message
+ Alt-T will edit message text directly
+ You can now start in the arealist function when you enter an area
+ Default directory file-attach/import file can be defined
+ More information on area statistics including quote-ratio
+ HIDE command in TM.BBS will not show area in area-selection menu
+ Semaphores: TMRESCAN.NOW, TMFREEZE.NOW, TMNOTE.NOW
+ F11 now allow you to search the nodelist with keyword or address
+ KeepSoftReturns, do not strip #141 (soft-returns) from messages
+ New keyword: NeverToss. Never toss incoming mail or ask.
+ /LINK will link all areas. /LINK areaname will only link 1 area
* Searchmenu can now search both forward and backwards

